agAdapter(adaptedParent));\\n\\n        JspTag ancestor = SimpleTagSupport.findAncestorWithClass(child, SimpleTagSupport.class);\\n\\n        assertThat(ancestor).isSameAs(adaptedParent);\\n    }\\n}\\n\"}], \"isError\": false, \"timestamp\": 1777670974181}]}\nhuman-intervention-logs/jspapi:jsp-api:2.0-20040521/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-01T21-23-10-339902Z.log:11620:[assistant] - Added coverage for the `TagAdapter` unwrapping path in `SimpleTagSupport.findAncestorWithClass(...)`.\nhuman-intervention-logs/jspapi:jsp-api:2.0-20040521/add-new-library-support/pi-generation-2026-05-01T21-23-10-339902Z.log:11625:[recv] {\"type\": \"message_end\", \"message\": {\"role\": \"assistant\", \"content\": [{\"type\": \"thinking\", \"thinking\": \"\", \"thinkingSignature\": \"{\\\"id\\\":\\\"rs_0cffb71c604539cd0169f51b3f7794819ca58127ac5b156066\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"reasoning\\\",\\\"encrypted_content\\\":\\\"gAAAAABp9Rs_xV9DQbDiMWMAgeRButDtn4PVFp3-foXgvNki27IQ0IcJ2zaXmaMkYTd1nww-cjfWA195wrvyQyVtJ0egpEbwT6U5EEjr1_tVXCTGXChQ1zssRsrncDphY16rLiFcdoH9jjNz0z_nk1OlNMRCqm-NHrTlYBGIEspOe5UyUGKVVIi6tGHu5k7w1Kdj3ScQ5e_w6BniafcZL_eL6vGEATYaaOXU_ZwNFtC2ANybkyxKikJfJSQDZRDjIeEk3r1NgrWKNZSIubGaGwPo2vBCsyAlZHuKIr_UDofbdzmBojlHX0cpPZ4T9p94pYitkT_vKnOBqhmSoOiOtjhrgAVYA8wagzgoQu5xRiVqrScbgDSAimk7tTlOl9VT2YSBfUQumm7dFVnYB3CMaJSgGMy7eMf1u35AB18W6N1GEDNN8S8sm6ZQkDQWV-pCXsx9grwW0OxP4ef682Igqr8ifi-dY6F1n-AL6hViT72syznHJkgyhIF_oO6YlnwHhZpg2GVDvq_nA6oOzayaci4-vmUy0IA76cyoLDBq5yKcju1MDOTjFquDApboWQy2JigGIvOKhO1nqDnbfSQsf9aqtVwFsMcCzZmDbclsPJeATdjDE-BZg8EbFrM9nKp4M1N80Bc3X6CxAGpT7QrGKcB-3Gr1Y24p8eEM7R5f_7jgnijqjQZsZY44vCbi0ujHk8NRZgGGnMUvgHA37t2IyzXU5-AVoeP9wiholn9rH9-hrJrO0BiGsbHz0vyz5VrhlDuydXpWwM5u3-22PJVlLNgdqvMasz1j5Z8froUHTufZ9yGST9Baz2L-EKos-khqvq9IRXA_K9z65mxVMObM7v4O4_sUTvBK2GPIF1YaNQxI5xyezs4PNkQXS6xNCTbltjUr9YH99EUFnUV-Gvmd3cpphf5LPjss_kP4LX4ZfyNGKbz8azjYRVG1gZmMbjVo9W-nKKEAPCrn\\\",\\\"summary\\\":[]}\"}, {\"type\": \"text\", \"text\": \"Refined the dedicated active-class test